descriptions:
I'm a software developer and I suck at skateboarding.
The open source project I currently mostly work on is "CollabThings" (https://github.com/CollabThings). It's a platform to store, share in a designs of machines and constructions, scripts and instructions how those are manufactured and maintained. Everything is parts linked together and every piece is automatically shared through waazdoh -network
I feel strongly about equality and human rights, love science and technology and I think people should think again what is causing the problems in societies and what is "right" and "justified".
Most of the things I do and share is on my Google+ feed.
... and you should watch Zeitgeist: Moving Forward https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Z9WVZddH9w
My projects in Sonar: http://ci.waazdoh.com/sonar
Being a nerd and I dreaming of a better world.
